SERVER_PORT_INTERSYMBOL_TIME_VEC

public static int[] SERVER_PORT_INTERSYMBOL_TIME_VEC
The ports associated with specific, pre-set, inter-symbol times are ports 46101, 46102, etc. This array gives the inter-symbol times associated with those ports (as well as determining how many of them will exist). Consecutive values in the array correspond to ports 46101, 46102, etc.
